#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:69
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Upoznavanje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:70
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "&ark; is a program for viewing, extracting, creating and modifying "
#| "archives. &ark; can handle various archive formats such as <command>tar</"
#| "command>, <command>gzip</command>, <command>bzip2</command>, "
#| "<command>zip</command>, <command>rar</command>, <command>7zip</command>, "
#| "<command>xz</command>, <command>rpm</command>, <command>cab</command> and "
#| "<command>deb</command> (support for certain archive formats depend on the "
#| "appropriate command-line programs being installed)."
msgid ""
"&ark; is a program for viewing, extracting, creating and modifying archives. "
"&ark; can handle various archive formats such as <command>tar</command>, "
"<command>gzip</command>, <command>bzip2</command>, <command>zip</command>, "
"<command>rar</command>, <command>7zip</command>, <command>xz</command>, "
"<command>rpm</command>, <command>cab</command>, <command>deb</command>, "
"<command>xar</command> and <command>AppImage</command> (support for certain "
"archive formats depends on the appropriate command-line programs being "
"installed)."
msgstr ""
"&ark; je program za gledanje, ekstraktovanje, kreiranje i modificiranje "
"arhiva. &ark; može upravljati sa više formata arhiva kao što su "
"<command>tar</command>, <command>gzip</command>, <command>bzip2</command>, "
"<command>zip</command>, <command>rar</command>, <command>7zip</command>, "
"<command>xz</command>, <command>rpm</command>, <command>cab</command>i "
"<command>deb</command> (odrška za određene formate arhive zavisi od "
"prikladnosti komandne linije programa koji je instaliran)."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:85
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "<phrase>&ark;'s main window</phrase>"
msgid "&ark;'s main window"
msgstr "<phrase>&ark;'s glavi prozor</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:89
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "In order to successfully use &ark;, you need &kde; 4. &GNU; <command>tar</"
#| "command> and a recent <command>gzip</command> are also needed if you want "
#| "&ark; to handle tar archives. To handle other file formats, you need the "
#| "appropriate command line programs, such as <command>bzip2</command>, "
#| "<command>zip</command>, <command>unzip</command>, <command>ar</command>, "
#| "<command>rar</command>, <command>7zip</command>, <command>xz</command>, "
#| "<command>rpm</command>, <command>cab</command> and <command>deb</command>."
msgid ""
"In order to successfully use &ark;, you need KDE Frameworks 5. The library "
"libarchive version 3.1 or above is needed to handle most archive types, "
"including tar, compressed tar, rpm, deb and cab archives. To handle other "
"file formats, you need the appropriate command line programs, such as "
"<command>zipinfo</command>, <command>zip</command>, <command>unzip</"
"command>, <command>rar</command>, <command>unrar</command>, <command>7z</"
"command>, <command>lsar</command>, <command>unar</command> and "
"<command>lrzip</command>."
msgstr ""
"U smislu ispravnog korištenja &ark; potrebno vam je &kde; 4. &GNU; "
"<command>tar</command> i predhodni <command>gzip</command> su također "
"potrebni ako želite &ark;  da upravlja arhivom. Da biste upravljali drugim "
"fajl formatima, potrebno vam je odgovarajuči red komandi u programu, kao što "
"su <command>bzip2</command>, <command>zip</command>, <command>unzip</"
"command>, <command>ar</command>, <command>rar</command>, <command>7zip</"
"command>, <command>xz</command>, <command>rpm</command>, <command>cab</"
"command> and <command>deb</command>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:100
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using &ark;"
msgstr "Korištenje &ark;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:103
#, no-c-format
msgid "Opening Archives"
msgstr "Otvaranje Arhive"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:105
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "To open an archive in &ark;, choose <guimenuitem>Open...</guimenuitem> "
#| "(<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>O</keycap></keycombo>) from the "
#| "<guimenu>File</guimenu> menu. You can also open archive files by dragging "
#| "and dropping from &konqueror; or &dolphin;. Archive files should be "
#| "associated with &ark;, so you can also <mousebutton>right</mousebutton> "
#| "click a file in &konqueror; or &dolphin; and select <guimenuitem>Open "
#| "with &ark;</guimenuitem> to open it or select an extract action for this "
#| "file."
msgid ""
"To open an archive in &ark;, choose <guimenuitem>Open...</guimenuitem> "
"(<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>O</keycap></keycombo>) from the "
"<guimenu>Archive</guimenu> menu. You can also open archive files by dragging "
"and dropping from &dolphin;. Archive files should be associated with &ark;, "
"so you can also <mousebutton>right</mousebutton> click a file in &dolphin; "
"and select <guimenuitem>Open with &ark;</guimenuitem> to open it or select "
"an extract action for this file."
msgstr ""
"Da biste otvorili arhivu &ark;, izaberite <guimenuitem>Otvori...</"
"guimenuitem> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>O</keycap></"
"keycombo>) iz <guimenu>Fajl </guimenu> izbornik. Također možete otvoriti "
"arhivu fajlova premještanje iz &konqueror; ili &dolphin;. Arhivirani fajlovi "
"bi trebali biti povezani sa  &ark;, tako da možete također <mousebutton> "
"desni </mousebutton> kliknuti na fajl u &konqueror; ili &dolphin; i "
"selektovati <guimenuitem> Otvoreno sa &ark;</guimenuitem> da biste otvorili "
"oto ili selektovati ekstraktovanu akciju iz ovog fajla."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:113
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have enabled the information panel in the <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> "
"menu additional information about the selected folders or files in the "
"archive is displayed."
msgstr ""
"Ako ste omogućili panela informacija u <guimenu> Postavke </guimenu> "
"izbornik za dodatne informacije o selektovanom folderu ili fajlu u arhivi je "
"prikazano."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:117
#, no-c-format
msgid "Archive Operations"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:119
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Various operations can be performed for an opened archive by using the "
"<guimenu>Archive</guimenu> menu. For example, you can save the archive with "
"a different name using <guimenuitem>Save As...</guimenuitem>. Archive "
"properties such as type, size and MD5 hash can be viewed using the "
"<guimenuitem>Properties</guimenuitem> item."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:124
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&ark; has the ability to test archives for integrity. This functionality is "
"currently available for <command>zip</command>, <command>rar</command> and "
"<command>7z</command> archives. The test action can be found in the "
"<guimenu>Archive</guimenu> menu."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:131
#, no-c-format
msgid "Archive Comments"
msgstr ""

