"Da biste kreirali novu arhivu u &ark;, izaberite <guimenuitem>Novo</"
"guimenuitem> iz <guimenu> Fajl </guimenu>izbornik."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:147
#, no-c-format
msgid "Editing a comment"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:151
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The comment menu item is enabled only for <literal role=\"extension\">rar</"
"literal> archives."
