"fajl iz &konqueror;, &dolphin; na vaš ekranu u glavni &ark;  prozor, i bit "
"će dodano u trenutnu arhivu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:317
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Additional options are presented in collapsible groups at the bottom of the "
"dialog."
